reviewText: Mty previous copy of this was overdubbed u saved me bacon 10/10 took me a good few years to collect the awa vhs well done to us both.

The tape is recorded in the SP mode and while only 30 minutes long, contains 3 classic matches:
1. Road Warriors vs. Long Riders
2. Road Warriors vs. a couple of jobbers
3. Road Warriors vs. Regal/Garvin (Title
change when Freebirds interfere).
